        <h3>What do the colors mean on the session listing?</h3>
        <p>The colors on the session listing are meant to give you a quick idea how full a given session is.</p>
        <p>Possible colors:
          <div class="label label-default">0</div> This (lack of) color means the workshop is full and cannot accept new members.<br>
          <div class="label label-danger">0</div> This color means the workshop is more than 3/4 full.<br>
          <div class="label label-warning">0</div> This color means the workshop is more than 1/2 full.<br>
          <div class="label label-success">0</div> This color means the workshop is less than 1/2 full.<br>
        </p>

